{"tid":32323,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"本民前　黃台仰　離港赴台出席　世界人權日活動","createTime":"2016-12-10T06:19:50.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-10T06:35:39.000Z","uid":47714,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4ee1aa85b31e62fa6bf9f69f1e908deae78421a6","tid":32323,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T06:19:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.localpresshk.com/2016/12/ray-wong/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.localpresshk.com%2F2016%2F12%2Fray-wong%2F&d=smYIAVCoBVBp%2BjayXsyke2N6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=e7cc0266\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.localpresshk.com/2016/12/ray-wong/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.localpresshk.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/1209_ray.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.localpresshk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F12%2F1209_ray.jpg&h=cbb4b767&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在農曆年初旺角衝突中，被控參與非法暴動的本土民主前線發言人黃台仰，早前申請更改保釋條件短暫離開香港，高等法院今日（九日）在控方不反對下，批准他今日起至本月十八日離港。他表示，將代表本民前到台灣參加世界人權日嘉年華的會議及公開活動。<br />\n<br />\n黃台仰及本民前另一發言人梁天琦，以及另外八名男子，分別被控參與及煽動暴動等罪名，案件已排期至二零一八年一月十五日開審。"},{"pid":"aff379b94b6618fe4de92d3075fffbd3e0bd98df","tid":32323,"uid":33408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T06:35:39.000Z","msg":"熱狗又嬲嬲豬呀"}]}